{"id":191715,"type":1,"name":"背の眼","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/34/04/191715_Y6Bz9.jpg","summary":"　　改编自同名小说的恐怖漫画。\r\n　　作家道尾一个人到名为「白峠」的小村庄度假，但是却不断听到奇怪的声音，加上村里流传的天狗传说，更使道尾感觉到诡异，于是寻求大学同学现在正经营「真备灵异现象探求所」的帮助。而真备恰巧收到四张灵异照片：照片中的人物背上出现一双眼睛。而这些背上出现眼睛的人们皆已自杀，且都去过这一个叫做「白峠」的村落……这个有着美丽风景的村子究竟隐藏着什么秘密呢？","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>背之眼</li><li><span>册数: </span>3</li><li><span>话数: </span>15</li><li><span>作画: </span><a href=\"/person/7583\">小池ノクト</a></li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/8371\">幻冬舎コミックス</a></li><li><span>连载杂志: </span>月刊コミックバーズ(<a href=\"/person/7585\">月刊バーズ</a>)</li><li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/13636\">道尾秀介</a></li><li><span>开始: </span>2008-07-31(2008年09月号)</li><li><span>结束: </span>2009-11-30(2009年11月号)</li>","collection":{"wish":2,"collect":3,"doing":1},"tags":[{"name":"漫画","count":2},{"name":"小说改","count":2},{"name":"小池ノクト","count":1},{"name":"マンガ","count":1},{"name":"道尾秀介","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":7583,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/86/c2/7583_prsn_76fxp.jpg","name":"小池ノクト","desc":"作画"},{"id":8371,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/e0/a5/8371_prsn_OCowB.jpg","name":"幻冬舍Comics","desc":"出版社"},{"id":7585,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/90/95/7585_prsn_8xCh8.jpg","name":"月刊バーズ","desc":"连载杂志"},{"id":13636,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/b5/2e/13636_prsn_VwYZL.jpg","name":"道尾秀介","desc":"原作"}],"relations":[{"id":191720,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/07/0a/191720_jp.jpg","title":"背の眼","type":"书籍","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/191720"},{"id":191716,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/5d/f7/191716_jp.jpg","title":"背の眼","type":"不同版本","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/191716"}],"comic":[{"id":191719,"name":"背の眼 (1)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/d0/2d/191719_jp.jpg"},{"id":191717,"name":"背の眼 (2)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/6e/42/191717_jp.jpg"},{"id":191718,"name":"背の眼 (3)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/55/be/191718_jp.jpg"}]}